{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"de19e847b3","title":"中央首长2月4日接见滕海清同志时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84b1d011d6","index":0,"year":1969,"month":2,"day":4,"articleId":"de19e847b3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"汪东兴","id":"3c11982f62","type":"人物"},{"name":"黄永胜","id":"440b5f1bc1","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"高锦明","id":"49002314ba","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"温玉成","id":"8d506eedf8","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"滕海清","id":"e616b0a976","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴法宪","id":"fa1994871e","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9a7b462f19","type":"title","text":"中央首长2月4日接见滕海清同志时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf8a7b2293","type":"subtitle","text":"【滕海清同志1969年2月8日在常委扩大会上传达记录整理】","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b38cb53ee9","type":"paragraph","text":"2月4日晚8时至12时，中央文革碰头会同志，有总理、伯达、康生、江青、张春桥、姚文元、谢富治、黄永胜、吴法宪、汪东兴、温玉成同志接见了滕海清同志。现将滕司令员传达记录整理如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3da0139ee8","type":"paragraph","text":"我简单的向中央文革汇报了自治区文化大革命情况。中央首长对内蒙的文化大革命是非常了解的，非常关心的。给我们很大的鼓励。对内蒙各族人民和解放军给了很高的评价。当然，我们在实际工作中还存在许多缺点。下边传达中央首长的指示：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fbce0d211","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们10月3日的电报，请示增加副主任、常委、委员问题，我看过了。我认为增加副主任、常委还要再看一看，在清理阶级队伍以后再增加更有把握些，所以没有批。不仅内蒙一个地区没批，其他省市早报了也没有批，包括北京、上海报来的也没有批。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9b326ee4b","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元同志：内蒙清理阶级队伍搞的比较早，也有不少经验。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f11154ed4","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：内蒙敌人很多，有伪满时代的，有蒙疆的，有付作义的，还有乌兰夫的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46890fda7a","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治同志：乌兰夫包庇了不少坏人。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3046737411","type":"paragraph","text":"这时，康老拿出了分电报说，你们发了个电报，说我们对挖内人党问题有个电报指示，我没记得发过这么个电报，是不是我们内部传达的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce3453dadd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们不要把我们某些讲话作为指示。滕说中央的批示，我们要坚决执行。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0ed0b1b14","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：内蒙很复杂，内部有敌人，外部有修正主义。乌兰夫在内蒙搞了20年，他要搞独立王国。内蒙问题，要全部解决，有个时间问题。你们时间不长，搞的不错嘛。你们不要太急了。中央从来没有催你们，有些地方，我们说他们怕步子太慢了，你们那儿，我们怕步子太快了。清理阶级队伍，要注意学习政策，扩大教育面、缩小打击面。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"285b672715","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：革委会刚建立起来，混进少数坏人是难免的，只要领导心中有数，没有什么了不起。对这些坏人可以不采取很快做组织处理，防止反扑。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41ac56fbdd","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥同志：你们内蒙形势好，对这些人处理没什么影响，在其他地区可能有反复。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a0477c01b","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥同志：不要只看内蒙问题，可能对外部有影响，起码对山西有影响。要顾全大局，防止阶级敌人对革委会个个击破。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"175d4c13e6","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：内人党是专门搞破坏活动的。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd1b1e1e17","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对内人党的首要分子，也要做争取教育，总会有个别分子起义。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"222be3198d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：内人党一般党徒，只要登记清楚，就行了，扩大教育面，缩小打击面。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0ce967578","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治同志：内人党哪里是共产党，哪里是内人党，要把它搞掉。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea8fb15878","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：军队也有内人党，这个问题很严重。这样的部队要改造，那有内人党的部队，你们能掌握吗？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f495e6aed","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：你们边防线那么长，骑兵到处跑，怎么得了。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d15c15e86a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：内蒙就像拉丁美洲的智利那样长，打起仗来怎么指挥？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5123f1cb38","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：已经有了个决定，准备把两头划出去。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70f59f8dde","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：有这个决定，我还不知道。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea52c9aa97","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：文化大革命以来，内蒙跑了多少人？蒙族有多少？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1e04a304a","type":"paragraph","text":"滕司令员说：没跑几个，蒙族有140多万人。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12e934750d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们比新疆少数民族还少嘛。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34ce8a4649","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：内蒙归北京军区领导，还是单独的？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b2e189f89","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：早就划给北京军区了。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"835401ed8b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：谢富治同志你是政治委员，你应该管。毛主席接见时你把滕海清同志忘了。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9c31d6600","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们在北京开会，对内人党问题要很好的研究一下。你们搞了个文件还不够，要搞一个好的文件给我们看一下。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7655cfa4cf","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：对一般党徒，要教育。蒙古族干部大多数是好的，他们加入内人党多数是受蒙蔽的。要教育他们回到毛主席革命路线上来。对蒙古族干部要培养，革委会要吸收一些贫下中农、贫下中牧参加进来。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"257ae9e6cc","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥同志：这个问题怎么搞法，又不能脱离生产，是否采取轮换办法。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5976589be","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥：我看内蒙古日报报头上没有蒙文，新疆日报有维吾尔文。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"affec34de9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要使人感到，乌兰夫打倒了，蒙文也不要了。现在内蒙是不是用斯拉夫文？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bace6745b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：乌兰夫会不会讲蒙古话？","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62805b380a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不会讲。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1091ba062b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：内蒙是很复杂的，敌人很多。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ec1e92b4d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：边防线这么长，敌人到处可以跑。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d60cd5dc22","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志：现在有通过沙漠的汽车。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c432094bff","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志：草原要很好保护，赫鲁晓夫把草原破坏了，现在还未恢复。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"487057372a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要很好的保护草原。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21e47349fe","type":"paragraph","text":"法宪同志：包头有几个国防工厂，要好好抓一下。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a46d085491","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：国防工业生产计划完不成，你们产值也完不成。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa6c1d46a3","type":"paragraph","text":"黄总长：你们要什么干部，写报告，可以调。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6511de337","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥同志：工厂有的工人领袖，要把他们提起来。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5caeedebb3","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：包头工业要抓一下。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b91b49025","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：乌达问题解决了没有？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64683fabdf","type":"paragraph","text":"滕说：解决了。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"819bccda4c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：河西公司问题解决了没有？","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2368d40df6","type":"paragraph","text":"滕说：两派已经联合起来，科研已经出了产品。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9553b16c2","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：河西公司我总感到是知识分子成堆的地方。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b877007cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们搞不好，对国家影响很大。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"944a221adb","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：呼三司头头叫什么？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0a063114c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：郝广德，现在怎么样？学生，开始造反时是有贡献的，但要注意他们爱搞当面一套，背后一套。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"731e2f660a","type":"paragraph","text":"滕司令员说：已经下放劳动了。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc382abe39","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对，要接受贫下中农的再教育。你们把劳改农场人员分散到各地，这个办法好。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"deb0ba88dc","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：高锦明的错误很严重，历史问题不清楚，还有三反言论，去年又搞了反复。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4918cc3e65","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：高锦明搞反复，当时你们常委怎么样？现在转过来了没有？","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b95bbc990","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：高锦明搞反复，就是看文流看多了，这样他必然要犯错误。历次群众运动总要出些毛病，是不可避免的。高锦明对文流问题看到了对你们有好处，使你们有警惕。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"24e94e8db2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：地方现在结合了多少干部？对结合的干部要有个政策。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e4c479a41","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥同志：地方干部胆子小，不敢大胆工作，你们要知道，人家犯了错误，怕再犯错误。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95522ab0f3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对这些干部要有个政策。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bcbb6748d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：今天就谈到这个地方。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a405eb97ed","type":"paragraph","text":"滕海清同志来北京很长时间了。一方面，我们工作安排不好，另方面，我们感到内蒙没有什么问题，这是主要的。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08189a2d09","type":"paragraph","text":"滕司令员说：我们生产建设兵团搞不搞？","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a33acb976","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这个问题已经解决了，毛主席已经批了。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d948df4a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"滕司令员说：国家没有给钱和物资。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7625e7bb47","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那好办，可以报一下。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa8d198fdc","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥；内蒙形势很好，清理阶级队伍成绩很大，应当肯定。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71ddda3ec7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：运动中出现些支流是难免的。高锦明的错误严重，要做检查。要把内人党组织搞垮、搞臭，打击少数，教育多数。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94dd8c0dc9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理问滕海清同志，你最近就回去吗？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e10d1e7e33","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥：他回去一下有好处。出来后谣言很多。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f7ef1aa7d","type":"paragraph","text":"2月3日还向军委办事组作了汇报，黄总长对军队工作有不少指示，另外给军区传达。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8202a48ec8","type":"paragraph","text":"滕说，中央对我们的工作，再三鼓励，我们不要骄傲自满。在北京已经给盟市负责同志讲了这个问题。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7119de399","type":"paragraph","text":"1969年2月","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"de19e847b3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}